# === CONFIGURACIONES SENSIBLES ===
# NOTE: the project's configuration folder is named with an accent: "configuración/".
# Previous entries referenced the misspelled directory "configuracion/" and caused
# confusion. Do NOT ignore the real `configuración/` directory or the tracked
# configuration files it contains (they are committed to the repository).
# If you need to ignore local-only config files, list them explicitly and avoid
# patterns that could match the repository's actual configuration files.
# (Keeping the old misspelled patterns for backward compatibility for local setups)
configuracion/*.backup
configuracion/*.temp
configuracion/.env
configuracion/config_local.json
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Ensure the actual accented folder and its committed files are not ignored
!configuración/
!configuración/*.json

